high_descs: Turn right, turn left at the sink, turn right at the wall and face the toilet.
Pick up a blue spray bottle from the back of the toilet.
Look down at the bin to the right of the toilet.
Put the spray bottles down in the bin.
Look up at the back of the toilet.
Pick up the spray bottle from the toilet.
Look down at the bin next to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle in the bin.
anns.task_desc: To move two spray bottles to the bin next to the toilet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the toilet in the far left of the bathroom.
On the shelf of the toilet, pick up the sprayer in the back.
Step back to be centered with the toilet.
Place the sprayer in the gray can on the right.
Step forward to the toilet.
Pick up the sprayer on the toilet.
Take a few steps back to see the gray can on the right.
Place the sprayed in the gray can to the right of the other sprayer.
anns.task_desc: Take two sprayers off the toilet and put them in the gray can.

high_descs: Go to your right and cross the room to the toilet.
Pick up the furthest spray bottle that is on the top of the toilet.
Look down to the floor.
Put the spray bottle in the trash can.
Look back up to the back of the toilet.
Pick up the other spray bottle from the toilet top.
Look down to the floor.
Put that one in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles in the trash can
